Purple ZNC Helper
=================

To install the plugin, simply run the included install script which copies the contents of the
archive to your .purple user dir (usually "~/.purple").

After activating the plugin you have to tick the option "Uses ZNC Bouncer" in the preferences of your IRC account in order to have it work with the specific account. Please make sure that you have set the timestamp format of ZNC to "[%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S]".

Have fun. :o)

Please note: You have to build the plugin from source in order to get a system wide installation!

